WEBVTT

00:08.467 --> 00:10.466
𝒯𝓇𝒶𝓃𝓈𝓁𝒶𝓉e 𝓊𝓃𝒾𝒸𝒶𝓉 E𝒩𝒢LI𝒮H

00:10.467 --> 00:11.465
<i>Previously on "Greenleaf"...</i>

00:11.467 --> 00:12.598
I'm looking for charity.

00:12.600 --> 00:13.598
Woman:
She's touring, singing.

00:13.600 --> 00:14.999
I came to apologize.

00:15.001 --> 00:16.332
I was wrong to leave like that.

00:16.334 --> 00:17.999
I'm ready to be a father again.

00:18.001 --> 00:20.198
Triumph has moved
very aggressively

00:20.200 --> 00:21.398
these last couple months.

00:21.400 --> 00:23.531
One of the things
we've been pressing forward on

00:23.533 --> 00:26.332
with a passion
is our outreach to the homeless.

00:26.334 --> 00:29.798
I'm interested in
more a personal connection.

00:29.800 --> 00:30.932
I've sensed that.

00:30.934 --> 00:32.865
I told that brother of mine
this'll never work.

00:32.867 --> 00:34.532
But you know what basie says.

00:34.534 --> 00:36.732
There's more than one way
to skin a Greenleaf.

00:36.734 --> 00:37.732
My mom knows we're having sex.

00:37.734 --> 00:39.399
What?!
Why are you mad at me?

00:39.401 --> 00:40.798
<i>I'm</i> in trouble.
You blamin' me?

00:40.800 --> 00:42.598
Isaiah.
You <i> really</i> blamin' me?

00:42.600 --> 00:44.399
I just saw Isaiah hit zora.
He did what?

00:46.001 --> 00:47.865
Zora?

00:47.867 --> 00:49.465
Kerissa!
Kerissa: What's wrong?

00:49.467 --> 00:50.732
Baby, she's not here.

00:50.734 --> 00:52.865
What do you mean she's not here?

00:52.867 --> 00:55.165
I forgive you.
You forgive me for what?

00:55.167 --> 00:56.265
James.

00:56.267 --> 00:59.765
For gettin' back at me
with him that one time.

00:59.767 --> 01:01.765
One time, really?

01:01.767 --> 01:03.865
I can't even count the times.

01:03.867 --> 01:05.865
I want you out of this house.

01:05.867 --> 01:07.598
Bishop, come on in.

01:07.600 --> 01:15.332
♪♪

